@ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7159

### Đăng ký Chủ quán
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Tran Thi B",
  "email": "business@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password1!",
  "userType": 1
}

### Đăng nhập
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "business@example.com",
  "password": "Password1!"
}

### Danh sách gói
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/plans

### Gói hiện tại
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/plans/current
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Tạo đơn chuyển khoản (QR + mã nội dung)
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/plans/purchase
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": 3
}

### Xem QR tĩnh (trình duyệt)
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/images/payment-qr.jpg

### Trạng thái đơn
GET {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### JWT sau khi Paid
POST {{ProxiJob.Identity.API_HostAddress}}/api/payments/1/session
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
